name: Tribal Tattoo
description: Bold, black designs often representing cultural heritage.

name: Small Tattoo
description: Basic, simple designs like a small symbol, word, or outline.

name: 3D Tattoo
description: Designs that appear to have depth and dimension, creating a lifelike effect.

name: Geometric Tattoo
description: Designs focusing on shapes and symmetry, requiring precision.

name: Cover-Up Tattoo
description: Tattoos designed to cover or replace an existing tattoo.

name: Visible Area Tattoo
description: Smaller designs in visible locations, often requiring more precision.

name: Sleeve Tattoo
description: Full-arm or leg designs covering a large area with complex elements.

name: Sleeve Touch-Up or Enhancement
description: Enhancing or freshening up an existing tattoo sleeve.

name: Medium Tattoo
description: Larger designs with more detail, typically fitting on the forearm or upper arm.

name: Dotwork Tattoo
description: Designs created with dot shading, often intricate and detailed.

name: Japanese Traditional Tattoo
description: Large, colorful designs with traditional themes, often covering significant body areas.

name: Portrait Tattoo
description: Realistic portraits, requiring a high level of detail and skill.

name: Cosmetic Tattooing (Permanent Makeup)
description: Makeup-like designs for eyebrows, eyeliner, or lips, often semi-permanent.

name: Custom Tattoo
description: Unique, personalized designs created specifically for the client.

name: Large Tattoo
description: Complex designs covering larger areas like the back, chest, or full sleeve.

name: Script/Lettering Tattoo
description: Text-based designs, varying with font choice and size.

name: Watercolor Tattoo
description: A style mimicking watercolor paintings, often colorful and abstract.

name: Color Tattoo
description: Tattoos with multiple colors, requiring more time and skill.

name: Minimalist Tattoo
description: Simple, clean designs with few lines and no shading.

name: Black and Grey Tattoo
description: Shaded designs with a more classic or realistic look.
